content.html:
Expert bladesmiths and skilled martial artists bring their custom, historical blades to the most punishing knife course ever created. Will a Wakizashi sweep away the competition? Or will the Parang emerge victorious? And can a Sundang Sword stay sharp? The final two competitors go head-to-head on the intimidating second course – “Dead Run”. Only one can advance to the finale, and compete for the chance to win $20,000 and the title of Knife or Death Champion
